About Us
Wafra Partners has developed an investment approach that provides the communication and flexibility required to address the varying needs of sellers and management partners in each transaction.






Benefits of our approach


                    Timely Response
                    Fair Valuation
                    Appropriate Capital Structure 
                

                    Proven Closing Capabilities
                    Management Equity Participation
                    Strategic & Analytical Support 
                

                    Board Level Participation
                    Long-Term Growth Orientation
                    Additional Capital for Future Needs 
                





Wafra Partners has been providing capital and strategic and operating support to middle market businesses & their management teams since 1990*.
We partner with management teams in seeking to build equity value through four key objectives: (i) accelerate growth, both organically and through acquisition; (ii) improve operating efficiencies; (iii) enhance cash flow; and (iv) position for attractive exit alternatives.





When considering a specific investment opportunity, typically important criteria include:

A strong and committed management team with significant ownership opportunities post-closing
A leadership position in technology, product line, cost position or distribution channel
Growth opportunities, internal or by acquisition
Diversity of products/services, customers, markets and suppliers
















Over 25 years* of partnering with management teams to build stronger companies



Consolidation strategy in the middle market



Patient capital



Certainty to close



Focused on accelerating growth














WHY WAFRA?For Sellers
The cornerstone of our long-standing approach is partnering with exceptional management teams who aspire to achieve industry leadership.  Through our partnership, we provide strategic resources and capital, while management leads day-to-day operating decisions.  Our long-term strategic view not only can align the incentives of the management team with shareholders, but also allows management to share in the value they create.
Contact Us



WHY WAFRA?For Intermediaries
Intermediaries are critical to Wafra Partners’ long-standing success. We deeply value the trust of investment bankers, independent sponsors, business brokers, and other deal intermediaries who provide us with private equity investment opportunities. We offer candid and timely feedback with certainty to close.
Contact Us



WHY WAFRA?For Executives
We are always looking for accomplished executives who may be interested in full-time positions or advisory/board roles with our portfolio companies.  
                        Additionally, we welcome contact from accomplished executives interested in targeting fragmented, consolidating industry sectors and within the individual’s particular expertise.  This could be in either a direct operating or advisory capacity.
Contact Us





